lude any HTML tags in any field....We can only accept plain text message, thanks.</td></tr><tr><td class="lsdata1" align="right" width="20%"><strong>Reply-to Address:</strong></td><td class="lsdata1"><input type="text" name="email" size="40" value=""></td></tr><tr><td class="lsdata2" align="right"><strong>Category:</strong></td><td class="lsdata2"><select name="type"><option selected>Please pick one:</option><option>Script library</option><option>Mailing list archive</option><option>Altme archive</option><option>Articles</option><option>General / other</option></select></td></tr><tr><td class="lsdata1" align="right"><strong>Summary:</strong></td><td class="lsdata1"><input type="text" name="summary" size="50"><input type="text" alt="ignore this field" name="user-conf" value="" size="12" style="display:none"></td></tr><tr><td class="lsdata2" valign="top" align="right"><strong>Description:</strong><br>Please keep it<br>short and clear.</td><td class="lsdata2"><textarea name="description" rows="12" cols="60"></textarea></td></tr><tr><td class="lsdata1" valign="top" align="right"><strong>Code Example:</strong><br>Show the problem.<br><span style="font-style: italic; font-size: 90%; font-weight: bold">Have a solution?</span></td><td class="lsdata1"><textarea name="example" rows="8" cols="60"></textarea></td></tr><tr><td class="lsh" colspan="2"><input type="submit" name="submit" value="Submit Feedback"></td></tr></table></form><h2>Thanks!</h2></div></td></tr></table><div class="footer"><ul><li><a href="http://www.rebol.org/index.r">[Home]</a></li><li><a href="http://www.rebol.org/script-index.r">[Script library]</a></li><li><a href="http://www.rebol.org/aga-index.r">[AltME archives]</a></li><li><a href="http://www.rebol.org/ml-index.r">[Mailing list archive]</a></li><li><a href="http://www.rebol.org/art-index.r">[Articles]</a></li><li><a href="http://www.rebol.org/boiler.r?display=accessibility" accesskey="0">[Access keys]</a></li><li><a href="#reb-over">[Top]</a></li></ul